race.comment: LADY HALIME (2) was below best at her last start when 6th at Horsham following a third place finish (26.19) at this track two back. Comes through a solid form race last start. Has ability and looks hard to stop. READY ONE (1) goes very well this course and distance starting five times for two wins and two minors. Was out of the placings last time (25.70) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 4.5 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances. KRAKEN TOMMY (4) is a talented type who has been in the money at the last three starts, the latest finishing third (25.75) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Rates a winning chance on best. SCOTT MICAH (8) is a last start winner worth following up.
